â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”œâ”€â”€ ğŸ“„ htmlGenerator.ts
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   Purpose: Frontend (browser) adapter for the V2 HTML email generation service, extending `HtmlGeneratorCore`.
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   Details:
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   - Adapts `HtmlGeneratorCore` (from `src/shared/services/htmlGenerator.ts`) for the frontend.
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   - Overrides element generation (`generateElementHtml`) specifically for `button` and `image` types to:
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   - Detect placeholder content using an `isPlaceholder` utility.
â”‚   â”‚   â”‚       â”‚   - Render placeholder elements with specific styling and text cues (e.g., "(Link Required)").
