â”‚   â”‚       Purpose: Supabase Edge Function to create a new blog post.
â”‚   â”‚       Details:
â”‚   â”‚       - Handles HTTP POST requests with blog post data (title, slug, content, author, category, image_url, excerpt, published_at) in the JSON payload.
â”‚   â”‚       - Initializes Supabase client using environment variables.
â”‚   â”‚       - Validates that required fields (title, slug, content) are present.
â”‚   â”‚       - Inserts the validated post data into the `blog_posts` table.
â”‚   â”‚       - Returns the newly created blog post data (or an error message).
