â”‚   â””â”€â”€ ğŸ“„ import_map.json
â”‚       Purpose: Defines path aliases for Deno module imports within the Supabase Edge Functions.
â”‚       Details: Maps short aliases (like `@/`, `shared/`, `@shared/`) to their actual relative paths from this file's location (`src/backend/functions/`). For example, `@/` maps to `../../src/`, `shared/` maps to `./_shared/` (i.e., `src/backend/functions/_shared/`), and `@shared/` maps to `../../shared/` (i.e., `src/shared/`). This simplifies import statements in the Edge Function code.
â”‚       Usage: Used by the Deno runtime when executing functions in `src/backend/functions/` to resolve aliased imports. Referenced by `src/backend/deno.jsonc` (if present) and `supabase/config.toml`.
